  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Tales Beyond The Tomb”</strong> is a chilling episodic horror series that immerses players in the shadows of real-life cases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the gritty, atmospheric horror of the 80s and 90s, each episode simulates the frightening experiences of real people, mixing nostalgia with unrelenting suspense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>This is the first episode of the series:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.poster.avif?t=1753938245\" width=590 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.webm?t=1753938245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.mp4?t=1753938245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Episode 1: Pineville Night Stalker</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After her mother's unexpected death, Megan receives a call about a sudden and mysterious inheritance awaiting in the desolate town of Pineville. With her work friend, Lenny – she embarks on a journey that should be simple, but quickly turns into a web of danger and deceit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS Aesthetic</strong> — Step back in time with visuals inspired by classic horror films of the ’80s and ’90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photorealistic Graphics & Immersive Environments</strong> — Feel the dread with lifelike visuals and haunting settings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice Activity</strong> — Interaction system with your microphone (no microphone is needed to play, but this increases your interaction and involves a complete experience).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dialog Text System</strong> — Immerse yourself in the plot with dynamic, narrative-driven dialogues.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person exploration experience (walking simulator), where realism is fundamental. Navigate immersive locations, discover disturbing truths, and face your fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“Tales Beyond The Tomb”</strong> is a chilling episodic horror series that immerses players in the shadows of real-life cases. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the gritty, atmospheric horror of the 80s and 90s, each episode simulates the frightening experiences of real people, mixing nostalgia with unrelenting suspense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>This is the first episode of the series:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.poster.avif?t=1753938245\" width=590 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.webm?t=1753938245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288180/extras/68f51631de9ecc3f0668bee0c6fc8dd6.mp4?t=1753938245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Episode 1: Pineville Night Stalker</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After her mother's unexpected death, Megan receives a call about a sudden and mysterious inheritance awaiting in the desolate town of Pineville. With her work friend, Lenny – she embarks on a journey that should be simple, but quickly turns into a web of danger and deceit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VHS Aesthetic</strong> — Step back in time with visuals inspired by classic horror films of the ’80s and ’90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Photorealistic Graphics & Immersive Environments</strong> — Feel the dread with lifelike visuals and haunting settings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Voice Activity</strong> — Interaction system with your microphone (no microphone is needed to play, but this increases your interaction and involves a complete experience).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dialog Text System</strong> — Immerse yourself in the plot with dynamic, narrative-driven dialogues.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A first-person exploration experience (walking simulator), where realism is fundamental. Navigate immersive locations, discover disturbing truths, and face your fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
